high_descs: Turn left and walk to the end of the counter on the left, then face the coffee maker.
Take the mug out of the counter above the coffee maker.
Heat the mug in the microwave.
Place the mug on the cabinet to the left of the microwave, to the right of the salt shaker.

high_descs: Turn to the left, and move through the kitchen. Face the coffee machine on the counter.
Open the top cabinet and take out the cup. Close the cabinet.
Hold the cup and take a step to the left, look up to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the cup inside. Shut the door and then open it. Take out the cup.
Hold the cup and look down, then take a step to the left and look up to the cabinet.
Open the cabinet and place the cup inside.
anns.task_desc: Heat a cup and place it in the cabinet.
